v.0.8.7
 New - Create Views From Rooms
 -Elevation Option: this option should be selected with a plan view opened in the background so then it will list out all rooms visible in the acitive view.
                   elevation views will have adjusted siz of crop box to fit to the bounding box of the selected room.

Fix - Place Unplaced Rooms
-In order to get users' interaction by letting them pick a point in the workspace, all window forms should be closed.
This version will close the opened windows, allow users to pick a point and reopen the command windows with the saved settings.
